cast.overview: A timid magazine photo manager who lives life vicariously through daydreams embarks on a true-life adventure when a negative goes missing.

details.biography: Amy Stiller was born on September 8, 1961 in New York City, New York, USA. She is an actress and writer, known for Inside Amy Schumer (2013), Divorce (2016) and The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel (2017). She is the daughter of actors Jerry Stiller and Anne Meara and sister of actor/director Ben Stiller.
